JNC 19 Apr 2025

Added parallelization of the more time consuming parts of the code (make_postcorr and make_bpass) also fixed a bug in normalizing the amplitude bandpass in make_bpass. Separated out removing the off source baseline and applying the amplitude bandpass. Now the user can use either one or both or none.

Some details on the files in this commit are given below.

