fitsio.h  No change

longnam.h No Change

makefile No change

newcorr.h No change

plot_flagged.py  No change

plot_postcorr.py No change

Readme -- this file.

read_rawvis.py no change

stats.c -- No change

svfits.c -- No change

svfits_par.txt -- added the parameters related to the added options in svfits.c.

svio.h -- changes to accommodate the added options to svfits.

svsubs.c -- parallelized the more time consuming sections of the code, fixed some smaller bugs in normalizing the amplitude bandpass, added options to separate off_src subtraction and amplitude bandpass calibration.

utils.c -- No change
